course_title: Practical Aspects of Anesthesia Practice I
course_description: This course discusses practical issues pertaining to the anesthesiologist assistant and the practice of anesthesia. Covered topics include: social, regulatory, ethical and professional aspects of becoming an anesthesiologist assistant.
